My heart is deeply touched as I read these stories from different people who are affected or have wondered what went on. I am one of those people as I was born in 1963 and always noticed a difference about the Vietnam war compared to say the II WW.  My sympathy is roused for everyone who has had to suffer for what?  I pray God's blessing on all of you.<br>

